<plot>A short sci-fi satire set deep into the future when the sun is starting to burn out. Solar powered energy is causing major mechanical malfunctions, and life on earth as we know it, is in serious jeopardy. The story focuses on a housewife who encounters some of these bizarre malfunctions on a day when the sun takes a turn for the worse. And her very reality and existence is called into question.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?495436</url></doc>
